<h2 class="bold font-l">Mega Man 10</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Strike Man's stage takes place on a stadium, features enemies throwing balls, giant robot goalies, soccerballs, and other sport amenities. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
